### Mini Jira API 测试集合
### 使用 IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client 运行

### 1. 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "test123456"
}

###

### 2. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "testuser",
  "password": "test123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.data.token);
%}

###

### 3. 创建项目（需要登录）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "我的第一个项目",
  "description": "这是一个测试项目"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("project_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

###

### 4. 查看我的项目列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### 5. 创建任务（需要登录）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects/{{project_id}}/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "修复登录bug",
  "description": "用户无法登录系统",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

###

### 6. 查看项目任务列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/{{project_id}}/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### 7. 测试未授权访问（应该返回 403）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects

###

### 8. 测试无效 Token（应该返回 403）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token-here

###
